package etzhayyim:shionome;

// The shionome actor's executable interface. A single export returns the
// cross-asset capital-flow result as a JSON string — the same logical contract
// as the watatsuna/tsumugi core ABI, realized as a WASI Component-Model
// component built with componentize-py (ADR-2606014600 + ADR-2606072200).
//
// The result is an OBSERVATIONAL summary (net flow / rotation / regime); it
// carries no_trade=true and never a buy/sell signal or price target (トレードはしない, G2).
world shionome-actor {
  export compute: func() -> string;
}
